text: You know what this symbol means, do you not, anon?
Have you read Marx's poetry, friend?
I suggest you give it a look and beg to hear your thoughts. Mind that I too have read Marx and enjoyed some of his works.

"Since I can create no world"

Do you get who he is talking about now?
He is talking about Lucifer and quite explicitly identifying himself with him. Reread it with this in mind, especially the part about not being able to stop the waves.

Even though the author and the poetical character being separate is the first rule of poetry, here the case goes deeper. I have discussed this a few people far more knowledgeable on this than anyone on twitter, and sadly we have solid grounds to believe Marx was a satanist.
The one communist figure I am saddened never gets any mention nowadays is Leonid Brezhnev. If only you knew, friends!
He is one of the most interesting Soviets, his rule was connected with a return towards Stalinism and an attempt at reestablishing a cult of personality, which sadly failed.
Yes, I am "blackpilled", and by this I mean I am looking for an African queen to copulate with.
I have not eaten an avocado since ~2017
